	<tr bgcolor="#99CCFF"><td colspan="2">
	    <strong><em>Escaping in Python docstrings</em></strong>
	    &nbsp;&nbsp;
	    (<a href="http://structuredtext.sourceforge.net/spec/pep257.html#backslashes">details?</a>)
	<tr align="left">
